&lt;b&gt;.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;=\r\n/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D&#39;margin-left:.5in&#39;&gt;&lt;span style=3D&#39;font-si=\r\nze:10.0pt;\nfont-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black&#39;&gt;&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span=\r\n style=3D&#39;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\ncolor:black&#39;&gt;&=\r\nnbsp;&lt;br&gt;\nNow let us examine these 2 cases separately.&lt;br&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;\nCase =\r\n1: Eclipse/bondage does not even exist. So it does not increase/decrease.\nT=\r\nhere is nothing to discuss! :-)&lt;br&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;\nCase 2: Eclipse/bondage exis=\r\nts and some acts increase it and some decrease it.\nIt is not merely efforts=\r\n to &quot;overcome&quot; this eclipse/bondage that may\nincrease it. So many=\r\n other acts could increase it. Some people may have engaged\nin too many suc=\r\nh activities and accumulated so much eclipse/bondage/covering of\nthe innate=\r\n divinity that it may actually need a lot of effort to undo it!&lt;br&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;=\r\n/span&gt;&lt;span style=3D&#39;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\ncol=\r\nor:#1F497D&#39;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p class=3DMsoListParagraph style=3D&#39;te=\r\nxt-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2&#39;&gt;&lt;![if !supportLists]&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span\nsty=\r\nle=3D&#39;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:red&#39;&gt;&lt;span\ns=\r\ntyle=3D&#39;mso-list:Ignore&#39;&gt;4.&lt;span style=3D&#39;font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&#39;&gt;&nb=\r\nsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;![endif]&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style=3D&#39;=\r\nfont-size:10.0pt;font-family:\n&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:red&#39;&gt;Both the cas=\r\nes are true, and that is what\nmaaya is. But one is absolute truth, and anot=\r\nher is a perceiv