 that you are\nalready a victim of an incidence, a=\r\nnd hence implicitly you are contradicting\nthe non-duality. So in essence, i=\r\nt is a hypocrisy.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span\nstyle=3D&#39;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Ar=\r\nial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:black&#39;&gt;&lt;br&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;\nThis is just one example. De=\r\npending on the person, many such examples can be\ngiven, where pretensions o=\r\nf &quot;I am Self&quot; can be shattered and one will\nbeg &quot;forget abou=\r\nt Self. I am in deep trouble. Somebody please help me out\nof this situation=\r\n&quot;!&lt;br&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;\nIf one is established in Self and NO situation ever =\r\ndisturbs one&#39;s equanimity,\nonly then one is realized. Such a state is not e=\r\nasy to achieve as some\npseudo-Vedantins may suggest.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n=\r\n\n&lt;p class=3DMsoListParagraph&gt;&lt;span style=3D&#39;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;A=\r\nrial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;\ncolor:black&#39;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p class=3DM=\r\nsoListParagraph style=3D&#39;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2&#39;&gt;&lt;![if =\r\n!supportLists]&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span\nstyle=3D&#39;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;san=\r\ns-serif&quot;;color:red&#39;&gt;&lt;span\nstyle=3D&#39;mso-list:Ignore&#39;&gt;8.&lt;span style=3D&#39;font:7=\r\n.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&#39;&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;=\r\n![endif]&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;span style=3D&#39;font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\n&quot;Tahoma&quot;,&quot;sans-ser=\r\nif&quot;;color:red&#39;&gt;Perhaps what I can understand from you is that\nyou had read =\r\nthe views of many scholars or vedantins which have truly bugged\nyour mind, =\r\nand your vocabulary and language patterns too.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span\nstyle=3D&#39;fon=\r\nt-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;san