r\n them. Even those particles are made up of smaller\nparticles and a lot of v=\r\nacuum in between them. As you keep dividing, you will\nsee that things are m=\r\nade up of subtle portions of matter and a lot of vacuum.\nWhen you go to the=\r\n level of small particles, work by physicists such as\nHeisenberg, Broglie, =\r\nSchroedinger etc says that you can&#39;t even observe and\ndetermine the propert=\r\nies of those particles confidently without affecting them.\nThey may not eve=\r\nn exist as &quot;matter&quot; with specific location and\nmomentum or even a=\r\ns waves, independent of the observer.&lt;br&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;\nHowever, despite that =\r\n&quot;quantum mechanics&quot; reality at the subtlest\nlevel, we have normal=\r\n &quot;mechanics&quot; too. A lot of gross objects made up\nof&nbsp; those s=\r\nubtle particles are gross enough and obey some grosser laws of\nphysics (e.g=\r\n. Newton&#39;s laws). We can find their positions, momentum etc\naccurately and =\r\nmake them move deterministically.&lt;br&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;\nWhen one is designing a ca=\r\nr or a pulley system or a rocket, one can leave\nquantum mechanics and use n=\r\normal mechanics. However, when one is doing research\non bosons etc, one mus=\r\nt pay attention to quantum mechanics. Otherwise, one will\ncommit errors.&lt;br=\r\n&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;\nSimilarly, at the subtlest level, Self alone exists. Things th=\r\nat seem to exist\nmay not even exist independent of the observer. However, t=\r\nhere are also the\nlaws of karma that govern the grosser reality (body, heal=\r\nth, job, spouse,\nchildren, house, car, money etc). Rishis taught Adwaita Ve=\r\ndanta and also the\nlaws that govern the world of duality (e.g. the law of k=\r\narma).&lt;br&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;br&gt;\nWhen one&#39;s awareness focuses on gross objects and one=\r\n is working with the gross\nworld, one better leave &quot;quantum spirituali=\r\nty&quot; (Adwaita Vedanta) and\nfocus on normal spirituality. However,